
Ubuntu:
	sudo apt install git make stow curl

	Install Menlo.ttc to ~/.fonts

	fc-cache -v ~/.fonts

MacPorts:
	sudo port install stow curl



git clone URL_OF_THIS_REPO
cd dotfiles-public
make



Apply settings once:

	mystartup.sh

Or on each login with gnome autostart:

	make startup



Emacs:  M-x package-refresh-contents
	M-x package-install-selected-packages

Vim:    :PlugInstall

Git:    Set name + email in ~/dotfiles/gitconfig_user


